# Soccer Drill Designer

This project provides a single-page web app for laying out soccer drills. The layout matches the requested 1.55:1 pitch ratio with a separate menu bar that spans the full width of the page.

## Features
- SVG-based pitch that occupies roughly 70% of the vertical viewport with responsive scaling.
- Declarative menu data (`TOOL_GROUPS` in `script.js`) that populates selectable items such as players, cones, equipment, and arrows.
- Interactive actions that let you move, remove, resize, recolor, and place items on the pitch.

## Getting Started
Open `index.html` in any modern browser to launch the designer. The supporting CSS (`style.css`) and JavaScript (`script.js`) files are loaded automatically.

